Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己在干什么吗

Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂慰的帝国

Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特队队长亚伯力克·基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来报道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于嘉依卡 我队除当初追捕的一名外又增加一名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下正追踪两名嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他队有什么新情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前没什么实质上的进展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关长 我想再看一下贾兹皇帝的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些及其他从贾兹城收押的东西都保管在书库里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 事到如今还有什么好查的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伯力克 这五年来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对嘉依卡的案件一直很重视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但关于皇帝的详细情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话即便如今我们已经击杀了他 仍然对他不够了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡收集遗体的行为真会对我们造成威胁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个嘉依卡从我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走了阿巴尔特伯爵拥有的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的目的与「威胁」相差甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 祭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括有装铠龙与他们一同行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有些地方令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我实在看不出他们有颠覆国家的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是有些别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伯力克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从嘉依卡的案件抽手一段时间怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡的问题确实是很重要的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但目前 我们的首要职责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是实际改善大陆人民的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须以这为最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动大 操纵 难关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们特地选了条小路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这根本称不上是路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个将你和机车连接起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并通过魔法思念料驱动它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与机杖 同样构造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化石 矿石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体中所含生物的记忆 思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的思念料 一切魔法之源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾兹皇帝的遗体也是很强大的魔法思念料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长 你知道现今大部分魔法技术是谁发明的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是贾兹皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这机车和机杖 都是你爸发明的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 伟大的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交通行费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是新贾兹帝国的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0110,0040,,{\fs38}NeoGaz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得贾兹帝国 自从五年前皇帝被杀就灭亡了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是渴望复兴帝国之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现正与去世皇帝的遗孤 嘉依卡公主一同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此地建立新的帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊愕的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是将军马拉德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及大臣拉布鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是近卫队队长弗洛鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那位就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新贾兹帝国的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 嘉依卡喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无礼 要向嘉依卡公主多表敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且把通行费交了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行许可 申请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟拿银币出来 你脑子里在想些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一看你们很是可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们还得赶路…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要检查一下车内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是道具箱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是这城来那镇去的候鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在这个村子 明天在那个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家带去幸福的江湖卖艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江湖卖艺人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 也为了证明你们的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来给嘉依卡公主表演些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新贾兹城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不准何时又会有六国联盟的追兵前来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此这只是为瞒过世人眼睛的暂时的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以这里的皇帝之女嘉依卡公主为旗首
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以新贾兹帝国的复活为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫离开国家的贾兹帝国国民们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万众一心集结在了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者还另有对六国联盟心怀不满的有志之士们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在支持我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国复兴之日已近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天让大家欣赏几项我们的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于本事还未到家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有失误 还请多多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出的这个苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇 扔出去也不会落地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 怎么样 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这边的苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇 它会把飞向少女的匕首都吸过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在哪儿见过?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这只小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个只要施展咒语 就会显露出本性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乎其神的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌拉 乌拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌拉 乌拉 乌拉 乌拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌拉拉 乌拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了 那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全神贯注中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…这事不要太钻牛角尖比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人在等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于贾兹皇帝有弄明白什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说没什么有价值的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连他出生相关的情报都不明不白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为至少应该会有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝到死前一直着手的最前沿技术的资料的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么关于嘉依卡的事情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只听说有残党想拥立嘉依卡企图复兴帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有实际确认到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人 今天的用餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我今天从早上到现在还什么都没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吃个饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好棒的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街头艺人体力很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在棺材里放只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果一打开变成了装铠龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个戏法 到底是怎么办到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微透露一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛鲁 你喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里所有人 贾兹帝国国民?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你们也是贾兹帝国出身?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么不早说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我马上拿去换成军资金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了喔 同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了贾兹帝国的复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重振皇室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新贾兹帝国万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屁新贾兹帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了不就是一群盗贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经吃足一枚银币的饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要继续待下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 名字叫做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡和托鲁是什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的表演 两人配合好默契啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是兄妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 坚决否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新贾兹帝国 复兴 希望?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想给因战争而流离失所的贾兹帝国国民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供一处栖身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 我想重建帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有栖身之所 幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的 大家的幸福?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 芙蕾多妮卡也是贾兹人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能不能一起来帮忙复兴帝国?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去拜访资产家的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他们给予资金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要芙蕾多妮卡开口请求他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家都会慷慨解囊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮帮我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法忘怀的 有你的冬天的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等候 你那身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比冻结的吐息更清白的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比大地更清澈的蓝色眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚麻色的头发如琥珀般闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情诗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这是贾兹帝国的诗人的诗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想记下来吗 我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 你那如阳光般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将颤抖的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主 请移驾执务室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天再继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩儿是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再加把劲就能攻陷她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外两人交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把钱全弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那机车也一定不能放过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人有约不能走?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续和那帮家伙纠缠可没好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点赶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁正确
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那约定有这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会被那套新贾兹帝国建国的说辞骗到了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是收集父亲遗体吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定 接着反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚出发 明早出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差别无大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路况很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早再走较为明智
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且没嘉依卡开车 机车也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再出发也无妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性 道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是心太软了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉布鲁负责食堂的银餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿贮藏库里的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量挑些值钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是旧贾兹帝国的国民吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有意与我们一起复兴贾兹帝国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做江湖艺人 四处漂泊也很辛苦吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据你们的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证给你们相应的地位喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉失败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是普通的江湖艺人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过通缉令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡带着棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一头银色头发 有一对紫色眼瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:15:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要借嘉依卡这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起码先调查清楚再借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早说啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是曾经想说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才胡扯什么复兴贾兹帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是想也卷走我们的钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计你的同伴也都是这样骗入伙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本没想骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我们是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 目标太过遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是维持每日的生计就已经精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是被生活所迫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们也没有完全放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日会将帝国…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉德 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉娅她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们穿帮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉娅怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们彻底中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我问你尤莉娅去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的牢房里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没 明白了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不愿再添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭还是挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁 尤莉娅 救出 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫再牵扯较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉娅 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢房在地下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能带人从那里逃出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不可能的 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法使用 救出可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 努力 尤莉娅 救出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显现吧 沉默不语者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Silencer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正被六国联盟追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已才藏身此处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你出去 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你们不是来救我了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 要谢就谢嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢搭救之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔地包裹着颤抖的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以春天的光辉填满我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾兹的冬景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的你就是春天的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永不忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起 我欺骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡为什么旅行?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 祭悼 为了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你目标早日实现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是时候做个转变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的路又该怎么走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 再寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物归原主我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能问件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾兹皇帝是什么样的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如人品之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算问我 我连他长什么样都没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只听大家都说是个了不得的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们住在乡下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不清楚皇帝的事情 日子也是照样过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连那个他为了研发魔法技术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行了非常可疑的人体实验的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是战后才听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 实际情况我们一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还问这个做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是随便问问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们今后打算怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直拖延下来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候付诸行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连贾兹帝国的国民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不清楚皇帝的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸真是充满谜团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 他们今后打算怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 再发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是很严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派往加瓦尔尼公爵领
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求返还航天要塞索厄拉的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟被杀害 变成凄惨的尸体回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须立即进行武力制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法思念料 枯竭在即
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采购 必须
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天 终战纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店铺皆休息 我为难
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周 第九集 「记忆的价值」
 
