Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,// OPEDC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:05.79,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我们不要被条框锁住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:10.47,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼凑的时光又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:28.97,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了像今天这样的日子才叫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:39.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏过所有的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}恋爱笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:52.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手无策 在这深夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投无路 遵守着约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:02.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己镜中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我们不要被条框锁住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:13.76,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼凑的时光又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:20.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告别 这种答案毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:25.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只会继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:59.97,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}看看地狱之底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:07.54,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}小心别堕落下去 我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:22.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行尸走肉般走过的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:28.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}头顶的阳光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:33.54,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何时你已经沦落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:39.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}连自己名字也都遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:43.46,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人类 为何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.13,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:51.04,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}这无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:55.75,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如随之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:56.74,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}无常之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:08.16,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}从寸草不生的山谷向上攀爬 听风带来山林的回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:13.89,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}请看 指引我们的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:19.01,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}就是斩断悲哀的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:23.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}别害怕 别颤抖 活下去

